MORPH ENGLISH LEXICON (1.0)

-unknown  ADJ-S XLE (^ PRED) = '%stem';
          N-S XLE (^ PRED) = '%stem'
          "@CN".

+Noun   N-POS XLE "@CN".
+Sg     N-NUM XLE @SG-3PERS.
+Pl     N-NUM XLE @PL-3PERS.
+Token  N-POS XLE .
+Adj    ADJ-POS XLE .
+Verb   V-POS XLE .
+Pres   TNS XLE (^ TENSE) = pres.
+3sg    PERS XLE (^ SUBJ PERS) = 3
                 (^ SUBJ NUM) = sg.
+Non3sg PERS XLE (^ SUBJ NUM) = pl
                 { (^ SUBJ PERS) = 1
                 | (^ SUBJ PERS) = 2
                 | (^ SUBJ PERS) = 3 }.
+PastTense TNS XLE @MOOD-IND @ASPECT-SIMP @PAST.
+PastBoth TNS XLE @MOOD-IND @ASPECT-SIMP @PAST.
+123SP  PERS XLE .
+PresPart ASP XLE .
+Prog   ASP XLE .
+Prop  N-POS XLE .
+Giv   N-NUM XLE .
+Fem   N-NUM XLE .
+Masc  N-NUM XLE .
+Place  N-NUM XLE .
+Country N-NUM XLE .
+Fam   N-NUM XLE .

----

MORPH ENGLISH RULES (1.0)

V --> V-S_BASE
      V-POS_BASE
      { TNS_BASE
        PERS_BASE
      | ASP_BASE }.

N --> N-S_BASE
      N-POS_BASE
      N-NUM_BASE.

A --> ADJ-S_BASE
      ADJ-POS_BASE.

----